{"tid":2144704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人又係已經唔想再認真投入一段感情入面","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:03:31.000Z","uid":2342,"like":116,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"70d535330e559fa974d8a00c784334993875c987","tid":2144704,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"之前成日用情好深，毫無保留咁愛一個人<br />\n愛對方仲多過愛自己<br />\n自己既情緒永遠受對方所牽引帶動<br />\n<br />\n最後分左手，慢慢發現<br />\n其實自由自在咁生活都幾好<br />\n唔會受到另一半既約束，唔洗顧及人地既諗法<br />\n想去邊就去邊，想做咩就做咩<br />\n培養下唔同既興趣，認識下唔同既事物，見識下個世界<br />\n<br />\n生存係為左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2b5aec4584967832f6611bdb4b09db7b046e6f","tid":2144704,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90eef45dcdb40aa03d245f3a78da6a5338cd85f4","tid":2144704,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係你既選擇？"},{"pid":"7a660b165a08cbb7271af614166d114e98984877","tid":2144704,"uid":363621,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"覺得依家拍拖點都會散㗎啦 唔需要再咁投入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申讀緊u"},{"pid":"0cda6fe9aa73171df6eec824570fde26dd1c7e2f","tid":2144704,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90eef45dcdb40aa03d245f3a78da6a5338cd85f4","tid":2144704,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係你既選擇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"唔通唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24abc840165